        <h1>Moringa: The Miracle Tree for Health and Sustainability</h1>
        <p><strong>Moringa oleifera</strong>, often called the "Miracle Tree," is a fast-growing, drought-resistant plant native to South Asia and Africa. It has been used for centuries in traditional medicine and is now gaining global recognition for its exceptional nutritional value, medicinal properties, and environmental benefits.</p>

