        <ul>
            <li>Acts as a natural prebiotic, promoting good gut bacteria.</li>
            <li>Contains isothiocyanates, which help prevent ulcers and support stomach lining health.</li>
            <li>Anti-parasitic properties combat intestinal worms and infections.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>7. Natural Blood Sugar Regulator üí°</h2>
